var book = {
	"name": "2 Corinthians",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28785A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28785A\"></sup>an apostle of Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28785B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28785B\"></sup>by the will of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28785C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28785C\"></sup>Timothy our brother,To the church of God that is at Corinth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28785D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28785D\"></sup>with all the saints who are in the whole of Achaia:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28786E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28786E\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28787F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28787F\"></sup>Blessed be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28787G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28787G\"></sup>God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, the Father of mercies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28787H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28787H\"></sup>God of all comfort,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28788I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28788I\"></sup>who comforts us in all our affliction, so that we may be able to comfort those who are in any affliction, with the comfort with which we ourselves are comforted by God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For as we share abundantly in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28789J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28789J\"></sup>Christ's sufferings, so through Christ we share abundantly in comfort too.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28790K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28790K\"></sup>If we are afflicted, it is for your comfort and salvation; and if we are comforted, it is for your comfort, which you experience when you patiently endure the same sufferings that we suffer.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Our hope for you is unshaken, for we know that as you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28791L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28791L\"></sup>share in our sufferings, you will also share in our comfort.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For we do not want you to be unaware, brothers, of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28792M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28792M\"></sup>the affliction we experienced in Asia. For we were so utterly burdened beyond our strength that we despaired of life itself.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Indeed, we felt that we had received the sentence of death. But that was to make us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28793N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28793N\"></sup>rely not on ourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28793O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28793O\"></sup>but on God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28793P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28793P\"></sup>who raises the dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28794Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28794Q\"></sup>He delivered us from such a deadly peril, and he will deliver us. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28794R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28794R\"></sup>On him we have set our hope that he will deliver us again.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28795S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28795S\"></sup>You also must help us by prayer, so that many will give thanks on our behalf <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28795T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28795T\"></sup>for the blessing granted us through the prayers of many.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our boast is this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28796U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28796U\"></sup>the testimony of our conscience, that we behaved in the world with simplicity and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28796V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28796V\"></sup>godly sincerity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28796W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28796W\"></sup>not by earthly wisdom but by the grace of God, and supremely so toward you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For we are not writing to you anything other than what you read and understand and I hope you will fully understand—",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>just as you did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28798X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28798X\"></sup>partially understand us—that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28798Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28798Y\"></sup>on the day of our Lord Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28798Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28798Z\"></sup>you will boast of us as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28798AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28798AA\"></sup>we will boast of you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Because I was sure of this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28799AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28799AB\"></sup>I wanted to come to you first, so that you might have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28799AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28799AC\"></sup>a second <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28799AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28799AD\"></sup>experience of grace.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I wanted to visit you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28800AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28800AE\"></sup>on my way to Macedonia, and to come back to you from Macedonia and have you send me on my way to Judea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Was I vacillating when I wanted to do this? Do I make my plans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28801AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28801AF\"></sup>according to the flesh, ready to say “Yes, yes” and “No, no” at the same time?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>As surely as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28802AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28802AG\"></sup>God is faithful, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28802AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28802AH\"></sup>our word to you has not been Yes and No.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28803AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28803AI\"></sup>the Son of God, Jesus Christ, whom we proclaimed among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28803AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28803AJ\"></sup>Silvanus and Timothy and I, was not Yes and No, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28803AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28803AK\"></sup>in him it is always Yes.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28804AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28804AL\"></sup>all the promises of God find their Yes in him. That is why it is through him that we utter our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28804AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28804AM\"></sup>Amen to God for his glory.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And it is God who establishes us with you in Christ, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28805AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28805AN\"></sup>has anointed us,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and who has also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28806AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28806AO\"></sup>put his seal on us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28806AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28806AP\"></sup>given us his Spirit in our hearts as a guarantee.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28807AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28807AQ\"></sup>I call God to witness against me—it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28807AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28807AR\"></sup>to spare you that I refrained from coming again to Corinth.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Not that we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28808AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28808AS\"></sup>lord it over your faith, but we work with you for your joy, for you stand firm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28808AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28808AT\"></sup>in your faith."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>For I made up my mind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28809A\"></sup>not to make another painful visit to you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28810B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28810B\"></sup>if I cause you pain, who is there to make me glad but the one whom I have pained?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I wrote as I did, so that when I came I might not suffer pain from those who should have made me rejoice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28811C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28811C\"></sup>for I felt sure of all of you, that my joy would be the joy of you all.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28812D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28812D\"></sup>I wrote to you out of much affliction and anguish of heart and with many tears, not to cause you pain but to let you know the abundant love that I have for you.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28813E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28813E\"></sup>if anyone has caused pain, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28813F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28813F\"></sup>he has caused it not to me, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28813G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28813G\"></sup>in some measure—not to put it too severely—to all of you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For such a one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28814H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28814H\"></sup>this punishment by the majority is enough,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28815I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28815I\"></sup>you should rather turn to forgive and comfort him, or he may be overwhelmed by excessive sorrow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So I beg you to reaffirm your love for him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this is why I wrote, that I might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28817J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28817J\"></sup>test you and know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28817K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28817K\"></sup>whether you are obedient in everything.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Anyone whom you forgive, I also forgive. Indeed, what I have forgiven, if I have forgiven anything, has been for your sake in the presence of Christ,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>so that we would not be outwitted by Satan; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28819L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28819L\"></sup>we are not ignorant of his designs.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28820M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28820M\"></sup>I came to Troas to preach the gospel of Christ, even though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28820N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28820N\"></sup>a door was opened for me in the Lord,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>my spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28821O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28821O\"></sup>was not at rest because I did not find my brother Titus there. So I took leave of them and went on to Macedonia.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28822P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28822P\"></sup>thanks be to God, who in Christ always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28822Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28822Q\"></sup>leads us in triumphal procession, and through us spreads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28822R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28822R\"></sup>the fragrance of the knowledge of him everywhere.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For we are the aroma of Christ to God among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28823S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28823S\"></sup>those who are being saved and among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28823T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28823T\"></sup>those who are perishing,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28824U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28824U\"></sup>to one a fragrance from death to death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28824V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28824V\"></sup>to the other a fragrance from life to life. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28824W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28824W\"></sup>Who is sufficient for these things?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For we are not, like so many, peddlers of God's word, but as men of sincerity, as commissioned by God, in the sight of God we speak in Christ."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28826A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28826A\"></sup>Are we beginning to commend ourselves again? Or do we need, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28826B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28826B\"></sup>as some do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28826C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28826C\"></sup>letters of recommendation to you, or from you?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28827D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28827D\"></sup>You yourselves are our letter of recommendation, written on our hearts, to be known and read by all.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And you show that you are a letter from Christ delivered by us, written not with ink but with the Spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28828E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28828E\"></sup>the living God, not on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28828F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28828F\"></sup>tablets of stone but on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28828G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28828G\"></sup>tablets of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28828H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28828H\"></sup>human hearts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28829I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28829I\"></sup>Such is the confidence that we have through Christ toward God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28830J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28830J\"></sup>Not that we are sufficient in ourselves to claim anything as coming from us, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28830K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28830K\"></sup>our sufficiency is from God,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>who has made us sufficient to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28831L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28831L\"></sup>ministers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28831M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28831M\"></sup>a new covenant, not of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28831N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28831N\"></sup>the letter but of the Spirit. For the letter kills, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28831O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28831O\"></sup>the Spirit gives life.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28832P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28832P\"></sup>the ministry of death, carved in letters on stone, came with such glory <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28832Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28832Q\"></sup>that the Israelites could not gaze at Moses' face because of its glory, which was being brought to an end,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>will not the ministry of the Spirit have even more glory?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For if there was glory in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28834R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28834R\"></sup>the ministry of condemnation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28834S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28834S\"></sup>the ministry of righteousness must far exceed it in glory.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Indeed, in this case, what once had glory has come to have no glory at all, because of the glory that surpasses it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For if what was being brought to an end came with glory, much more will what is permanent have glory.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Since we have such a hope, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28837T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28837T\"></sup>we are very bold,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>not like Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28838U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28838U\"></sup>who would put a veil over his face so that the Israelites might not gaze at the outcome of what was being brought to an end.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28839V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28839V\"></sup>their minds were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28839W\"></sup>hardened. For to this day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28839X\"></sup>when they read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28839Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28839Y\"></sup>the old covenant, that same veil remains unlifted, because only through Christ is it taken away.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yes, to this day whenever Moses is read a veil lies over their hearts.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28841Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28841Z\"></sup>one turns to the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28841AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28841AA\"></sup>the veil is removed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now the Lord is the Spirit, and where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28842AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28842AB\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord is, there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28842AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28842AC\"></sup>freedom.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And we all, with unveiled face, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28843AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28843AD\"></sup>beholding <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28843AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28843AE\"></sup>the glory of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28843AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28843AF\"></sup>are being transformed into the same image <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28843AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28843AG\"></sup>from one degree of glory to another. For this comes from the Lord who is the Spirit."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28844A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28844A\"></sup>this ministry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28844B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28844B\"></sup>by the mercy of God, we do not lose heart.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But we have renounced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28845C\"></sup>disgraceful, underhanded ways. We refuse to practice cunning or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28845D\"></sup>to tamper with God's word, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28845E\"></sup>by the open statement of the truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28845F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28845F\"></sup>we would commend ourselves to everyone's conscience in the sight of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28846G\"></sup>if our gospel is veiled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28846H\"></sup>it is veiled to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28846I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28846I\"></sup>those who are perishing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>In their case <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28847J\"></sup>the god of this world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28847K\"></sup>has blinded the minds of the unbelievers, to keep them from seeing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28847L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28847L\"></sup>the light of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28847M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28847M\"></sup>the gospel of the glory of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28847N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28847N\"></sup>who is the image of God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28848O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28848O\"></sup>we proclaim is not ourselves, but Jesus Christ as Lord, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28848P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28848P\"></sup>ourselves as your servants for Jesus' sake.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For God, who said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28849Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28849Q\"></sup>“Let light shine out of darkness,” <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28849R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28849R\"></sup>has shone in our hearts to give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28849S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28849S\"></sup>the light of the knowledge of the glory of God in the face of Jesus Christ.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But we have this treasure in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28850T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28850T\"></sup>jars of clay, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28850U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28850U\"></sup>to show that the surpassing power belongs to God and not to us.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28851V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28851V\"></sup>afflicted in every way, but not crushed; perplexed, but not driven to despair;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>persecuted, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28852W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28852W\"></sup>not forsaken; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28852X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28852X\"></sup>struck down, but not destroyed;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28853Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28853Y\"></sup>always carrying in the body the death of Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28853Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28853Z\"></sup>so that the life of Jesus may also be manifested in our bodies.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For we who live are always being given over to death for Jesus' sake, so that the life of Jesus also may be manifested in our mortal flesh.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28855AA\"></sup>death is at work in us, but life in you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Since we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28856AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28856AB\"></sup>the same spirit of faith according to what has been written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28856AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28856AC\"></sup>“I believed, and so I spoke,” we also believe, and so we also speak,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28857AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28857AD\"></sup>he who raised the Lord Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28857AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28857AE\"></sup>will raise us also with Jesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28857AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28857AF\"></sup>bring us with you into his presence.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28858AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28858AG\"></sup>it is all for your sake, so that as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28858AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28858AH\"></sup>grace extends to more and more people it may increase thanksgiving, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28858AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28858AI\"></sup>to the glory of God.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So we do not lose heart. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28859AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28859AJ\"></sup>Though our outer self is wasting away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28859AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28859AK\"></sup>our inner self <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28859AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28859AL\"></sup>is being renewed day by day.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28860AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28860AM\"></sup>this light momentary affliction is preparing for us an eternal weight of glory beyond all comparison,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28861AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28861AN\"></sup>as we look not to the things that are seen but to the things that are unseen. For the things that are seen are transient, but the things that are unseen are eternal."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>For we know that if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28862A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28862A\"></sup>the tent that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28862B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28862B\"></sup>our earthly home is destroyed, we have a building from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28862C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28862C\"></sup>a house not made with hands, eternal in the heavens.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For in this tent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28863D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28863D\"></sup>we groan, longing to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28863E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28863E\"></sup>put on our heavenly dwelling,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>if indeed by putting it on we may not be found naked.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For while we are still in this tent, we groan, being burdened—not that we would be unclothed, but that we would be further clothed, so that what is mortal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28865F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28865F\"></sup>may be swallowed up by life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He who has prepared us for this very thing is God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28866G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28866G\"></sup>who has given us the Spirit as a guarantee.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So we are always of good courage. We know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28867H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28867H\"></sup>while we are at home in the body we are away from the Lord,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28868I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28868I\"></sup>we walk by faith, not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28868J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28868J\"></sup>by sight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Yes, we are of good courage, and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28869K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28869K\"></sup>would rather be away from the body and at home with the Lord.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So whether we are at home or away, we make it our aim to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28870L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28870L\"></sup>please him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28871M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28871M\"></sup>we must all appear before the judgment seat of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28871N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28871N\"></sup>so that each one may receive what is due for what he has done in the body, whether good or evil.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore, knowing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28872O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28872O\"></sup>the fear of the Lord, we persuade others. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28872P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28872P\"></sup>what we are is known to God, and I hope it is known also to your conscience.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28873Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28873Q\"></sup>We are not commending ourselves to you again but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28873R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28873R\"></sup>giving you cause to boast about us, so that you may be able to answer those who boast about outward appearance and not about what is in the heart.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For if we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28874S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28874S\"></sup>are beside ourselves, it is for God; if we are in our right mind, it is for you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the love of Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28875T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28875T\"></sup>controls us, because we have concluded this: that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28875U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28875U\"></sup>one has died for all, therefore all have died;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and he died for all, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28876V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28876V\"></sup>that those who live might no longer live for themselves but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28876W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28876W\"></sup>for him who for their sake died and was raised.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>From now on, therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28877X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28877X\"></sup>we regard no one according to the flesh. Even though we once regarded Christ according to the flesh, we regard him thus no longer.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore, if anyone is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28878Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28878Y\"></sup>in Christ, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28878Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28878Z\"></sup>a new creation. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28878AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28878AA\"></sup>The old has passed away; behold, the new has come.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>All this is from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28879AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28879AB\"></sup>who through Christ reconciled us to himself and gave us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28879AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28879AC\"></sup>the ministry of reconciliation;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>that is, in Christ God was reconciling the world to himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28880AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28880AD\"></sup>not counting their trespasses against them, and entrusting to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28880AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28880AE\"></sup>the message of reconciliation.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28881AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28881AF\"></sup>we are ambassadors for Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28881AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28881AG\"></sup>God making his appeal through us. We implore you on behalf of Christ, be reconciled to God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28882AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28882AH\"></sup>For our sake he made him to be sin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28882AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28882AI\"></sup>who knew no sin, so that in him we might become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28882AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28882AJ\"></sup>the righteousness of God."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28883A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28883A\"></sup>Working together with him, then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28883B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28883B\"></sup>we appeal to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28883C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28883C\"></sup>not to receive the grace of God in vain.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For he says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28884D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28884D\"></sup>“In a favorable time I listened to you,and in a day of salvation I have helped you.”Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28884E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28884E\"></sup>now is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28884F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28884F\"></sup>favorable time; behold, now is the day of salvation.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28885G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28885G\"></sup>put no obstacle in anyone's way, so that no fault may be found with our ministry,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28886H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28886H\"></sup>as servants of God we commend ourselves in every way: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28886I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28886I\"></sup>by great endurance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28886J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28886J\"></sup>in afflictions, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28886K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28886K\"></sup>hardships, calamities,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28887L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28887L\"></sup>beatings, imprisonments, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28887M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28887M\"></sup>riots, labors, sleepless nights, hunger;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28888N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28888N\"></sup>by purity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28888O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28888O\"></sup>knowledge, patience, kindness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28888P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28888P\"></sup>the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28888Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28888Q\"></sup>genuine love;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28889R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28889R\"></sup>truthful speech, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28889S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28889S\"></sup>the power of God; with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28889T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28889T\"></sup>the weapons of righteousness for the right hand and for the left;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>through honor and dishonor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28890U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28890U\"></sup>through slander and praise. We are treated as impostors, and yet are true;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>as unknown, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28891V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28891V\"></sup>yet well known; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28891W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28891W\"></sup>as dying, and behold, we live; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28891X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28891X\"></sup>as punished, and yet not killed;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28892Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28892Y\"></sup>as sorrowful, yet always rejoicing; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28892Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28892Z\"></sup>as poor, yet making many rich; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28892AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28892AA\"></sup>as having nothing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28892AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28892AB\"></sup>yet possessing everything.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>We have spoken freely to you, Corinthians; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28893AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28893AC\"></sup>our heart is wide open.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>You are not restricted by us, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28894AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28894AD\"></sup>you are restricted in your own affections.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28895AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28895AE\"></sup>In return (I speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28895AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28895AF\"></sup>as to children) widen your hearts also.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28896AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28896AG\"></sup>Do not be unequally yoked with unbelievers. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28896AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28896AH\"></sup>what partnership has righteousness with lawlessness? Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28896AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28896AI\"></sup>what fellowship has light with darkness?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28897AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28897AJ\"></sup>What accord has Christ with Belial? Or what portion does a believer share with an unbeliever?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>What agreement has the temple of God with idols? For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28898AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28898AK\"></sup>we are the temple of the living God; as God said,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28898AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28898AL\"></sup>“I will make my dwelling among them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28898AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28898AM\"></sup>walk among them,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28898AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28898AN\"></sup>I will be their God,and they shall be my people.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28899AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28899AO\"></sup>go out from their midst,and be separate from them, says the Lord,and touch no unclean thing;then I will welcome you,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28900AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28900AP\"></sup>and I will be a father to you,and you shall be sons and daughters to me,says the Lord Almighty.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Since we have these promises, beloved, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28901A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28901A\"></sup>let us cleanse ourselves from every defilement of body and spirit, bringing holiness to completion in the fear of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28902B\"></sup>Make room in your hearts for us. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28902C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28902C\"></sup>We have wronged no one, we have corrupted no one, we have taken advantage of no one.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I do not say this to condemn you, for I said before that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28903D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28903D\"></sup>you are in our hearts, to die together and to live together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I am acting with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28904E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28904E\"></sup>great boldness toward you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28904F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28904F\"></sup>I have great pride in you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28904G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28904G\"></sup>I am filled with comfort. In all our affliction, I am overflowing with joy.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28905H\"></sup>when we came into Macedonia, our bodies had no rest, but we were afflicted at every turn—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28905I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28905I\"></sup>fighting without and fear within.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28906J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28906J\"></sup>God, who comforts the downcast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28906K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28906K\"></sup>comforted us by the coming of Titus,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and not only by his coming but also by the comfort with which he was comforted by you, as he told us of your longing, your mourning, your zeal for me, so that I rejoiced still more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28908L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28908L\"></sup>even if I made you grieve with my letter, I do not regret it—though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28908M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28908M\"></sup>I did regret it, for I see that that letter grieved you, though only for a while.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As it is, I rejoice, not because you were grieved, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28909N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28909N\"></sup>because you were grieved into repenting. For you felt a godly grief, so that you suffered no loss through us.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28910O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28910O\"></sup>godly grief produces a repentance that leads to salvation without regret, whereas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28910P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28910P\"></sup>worldly grief produces death.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For see what earnestness this godly grief has produced in you, but also what eagerness to clear yourselves, what indignation, what fear, what longing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28911Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28911Q\"></sup>what zeal, what punishment! At every point you have proved yourselves innocent in the matter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So although I wrote to you, it was not for the sake of the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28912R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28912R\"></sup>who did the wrong, nor for the sake of the one who suffered the wrong, but in order that your earnestness for us might be revealed to you in the sight of God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28913S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28913S\"></sup>we are comforted.And besides our own comfort, we rejoiced still more at the joy of Titus, because his spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28913T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28913T\"></sup>has been refreshed by you all.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28914U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28914U\"></sup>whatever boasts I made to him about you, I was not put to shame. But just as everything we said to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28914V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28914V\"></sup>was true, so also our boasting before Titus has proved true.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And his affection for you is even greater, as he remembers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28915W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28915W\"></sup>the obedience of you all, how you received him with fear and trembling.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I rejoice, because I have complete <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28916X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28916X\"></sup>confidence in you."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>We want you to know, brothers, about the grace of God that has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28917A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28917A\"></sup>given among the churches of Macedonia,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for in a severe test of affliction, their abundance of joy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28918B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28918B\"></sup>their extreme poverty have overflowed in a wealth of generosity on their part.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For they gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28919C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28919C\"></sup>according to their means, as I can testify, and beyond their means, of their own accord,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>begging us earnestly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28920D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28920D\"></sup>for the favor of taking part in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28920E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28920E\"></sup>the relief of the saints—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and this, not as we expected, but they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28921F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28921F\"></sup>gave themselves first to the Lord and then by the will of God to us.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Accordingly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28922G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28922G\"></sup>we urged Titus that as he had started, so he should complete among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28922H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28922H\"></sup>this act of grace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28923I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28923I\"></sup>you excel in everything—in faith, in speech, in knowledge, in all earnestness, and in our love for you—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28923J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28923J\"></sup>see that you excel in this act of grace also.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28924K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28924K\"></sup>I say this not as a command, but to prove by the earnestness of others that your love also is genuine.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For you know the grace of our Lord Jesus Christ, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28925L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28925L\"></sup>though he was rich, yet for your sake he became poor, so that you by his poverty might become rich.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And in this matter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28926M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28926M\"></sup>I give my judgment: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28926N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28926N\"></sup>this benefits you, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28926O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28926O\"></sup>a year ago started not only to do this work but also to desire to do it.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So now finish doing it as well, so that your readiness in desiring it may be matched by your completing it out of what you have.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For if the readiness is there, it is acceptable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28928P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28928P\"></sup>according to what a person has, not according to what he does not have.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For I do not mean that others should be eased and you burdened, but that as a matter of fairness",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>your abundance at the present time should supply <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28930Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28930Q\"></sup>their need, so that their abundance may supply your need, that there may be fairness.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28931R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28931R\"></sup>“Whoever gathered much had nothing left over, and whoever gathered little had no lack.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28932S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28932S\"></sup>thanks be to God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28932T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28932T\"></sup>who put into the heart of Titus the same earnest care I have for you.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28933U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28933U\"></sup>he not only accepted our appeal, but being himself very earnest he is going to you of his own accord.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>With him we are sending <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28934V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28934V\"></sup>the brother who is famous among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28934W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28934W\"></sup>all the churches for his preaching of the gospel.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And not only that, but he has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28935X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28935X\"></sup>appointed by the churches to travel with us as we carry out this act of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28935Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28935Y\"></sup>grace that is being ministered by us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28935Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28935Z\"></sup>for the glory of the Lord himself and to show our good will.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>We take this course so that no one should blame us about this generous gift that is being administered by us,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28937AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28937AA\"></sup>we aim at what is honorable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28937AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28937AB\"></sup>not only in the Lord's sight but also in the sight of man.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And with them we are sending our brother whom we have often tested and found earnest in many matters, but who is now more earnest than ever because of his great confidence in you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>As for Titus, he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28939AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28939AC\"></sup>my partner and fellow worker for your benefit. And as for our brothers, they are messengers of the churches, the glory of Christ.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So give proof before the churches of your love and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28940AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28940AD\"></sup>our boasting about you to these men."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28941A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28941A\"></sup>it is superfluous for me to write to you about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28941B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28941B\"></sup>the ministry for the saints,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>for I know your readiness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28942C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28942C\"></sup>of which I boast about you to the people of Macedonia, saying that Achaia has been ready <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28942D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28942D\"></sup>since last year. And your zeal has stirred up most of them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28943E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28943E\"></sup>I am sending the brothers so that our boasting about you may not prove empty in this matter, so that you may be ready, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28943F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28943F\"></sup>as I said you would be.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Otherwise, if some Macedonians <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28944G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28944G\"></sup>come with me and find that you are not ready, we would be humiliated—to say nothing of you—for being so confident.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So I thought it necessary to urge the brothers to go on ahead to you and arrange in advance for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28945H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28945H\"></sup>gift you have promised, so that it may be ready <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28945I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28945I\"></sup>as a willing gift, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28945J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28945J\"></sup>not as an exaction.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The point is this: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28946K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28946K\"></sup>whoever sows sparingly will also reap sparingly, and whoever sows bountifully will also reap bountifully.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Each one must give as he has decided in his heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28947L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28947L\"></sup>not reluctantly or under compulsion, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28947M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28947M\"></sup>God loves a cheerful giver.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28948N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28948N\"></sup>God is able to make all grace abound to you, so that having all sufficiency in all things at all times, you may abound in every good work.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As it is written,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28949O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28949O\"></sup>“He has distributed freely, he has given to the poor;his righteousness endures forever.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He who supplies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28950P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28950P\"></sup>seed to the sower and bread for food will supply and multiply your seed for sowing and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28950Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28950Q\"></sup>increase the harvest of your righteousness.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28951R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28951R\"></sup>You will be enriched in every way to be generous in every way, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28951S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28951S\"></sup>through us will produce thanksgiving to God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the ministry of this service is not only supplying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28952T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28952T\"></sup>the needs of the saints but is also overflowing in many thanksgivings to God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>By their approval of this service, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28953U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28953U\"></sup>they will glorify God because of your submission that comes from your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28953V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28953V\"></sup>confession of the gospel of Christ, and the generosity of your contribution for them and for all others,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>while they long for you and pray for you, because of the surpassing grace of God upon you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28955W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28955W\"></sup>Thanks be to God for his inexpressible gift!"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28956A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28956A\"></sup>I, Paul, myself entreat you, by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28956B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28956B\"></sup>meekness and gentleness of Christ—I who am humble when face to face with you, but bold toward you when I am away!—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I beg of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28957C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28957C\"></sup>that when I am present I may not have to show <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28957D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28957D\"></sup>boldness with such confidence as I count on showing against some who suspect us of walking according to the flesh.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For though we walk in the flesh, we are not waging war according to the flesh.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28959E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28959E\"></sup>weapons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28959F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28959F\"></sup>our warfare are not of the flesh but have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28959G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28959G\"></sup>divine power <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28959H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28959H\"></sup>to destroy strongholds.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>We destroy arguments and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28960I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28960I\"></sup>every lofty opinion raised against the knowledge of God, and take every thought captive to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28960J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28960J\"></sup>obey Christ,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28961K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28961K\"></sup>being ready to punish every disobedience, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28961L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28961L\"></sup>when your obedience is complete.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28962M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28962M\"></sup>Look at what is before your eyes. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28962N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28962N\"></sup>If anyone is confident that he is Christ's, let him remind himself that just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28962O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28962O\"></sup>he is Christ's, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28962P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28962P\"></sup>so also are we.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For even if I boast a little too much of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28963Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28963Q\"></sup>our authority, which the Lord gave for building you up and not for destroying you, I will not be ashamed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I do not want to appear to be frightening you with my letters.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For they say, “His letters are weighty and strong, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28965R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28965R\"></sup>his bodily presence is weak, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28965S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28965S\"></sup>his speech of no account.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let such a person understand that what we say by letter when absent, we do when present.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Not that we dare to classify or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28967T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28967T\"></sup>compare ourselves with some of those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28967U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28967U\"></sup>are commending themselves. But when they measure themselves by one another and compare themselves with one another, they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28967V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28967V\"></sup>without understanding.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But we will not boast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28968W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28968W\"></sup>beyond limits, but will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28968X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28968X\"></sup>boast only with regard to the area of influence God assigned to us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28968Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28968Y\"></sup>to reach even to you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For we are not overextending ourselves, as though we did not reach you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28969Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28969Z\"></sup>For we were the first to come all the way to you with the gospel of Christ.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>We do not boast beyond limit in the labors of others. But our hope is that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28970AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28970AA\"></sup>as your faith increases, our area of influence among you may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28970AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28970AB\"></sup>greatly enlarged,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>so that we may preach the gospel in lands beyond you, without boasting of work already done in another's area of influence.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28972AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28972AC\"></sup>the one who boasts, boast in the Lord.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28973AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28973AD\"></sup>not the one who commends himself who is approved, but the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28973AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28973AE\"></sup>whom the Lord commends."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>I wish you would bear with me in a little foolishness. Do bear with me!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I feel a divine jealousy for you, since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28975A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28975A\"></sup>I betrothed you to one husband, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28975B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28975B\"></sup>to present you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28975C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28975C\"></sup>as a pure virgin to Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I am afraid that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28976D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28976D\"></sup>as the serpent deceived Eve by his cunning, your thoughts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28976E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28976E\"></sup>will be led astray from a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28976F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28976F\"></sup>sincere and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28976G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28976G\"></sup>pure devotion to Christ.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For if someone comes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28977H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28977H\"></sup>proclaims another Jesus than the one we proclaimed, or if you receive a different spirit from the one you received, or if you accept <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28977I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28977I\"></sup>a different gospel from the one you accepted, you put up with it readily enough.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Indeed, I consider that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28978J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28978J\"></sup>I am not in the least inferior to these super-apostles.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28979K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28979K\"></sup>Even if I am unskilled in speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28979L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28979L\"></sup>I am not so in knowledge; indeed, in every way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28979M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28979M\"></sup>we have made this plain to you in all things.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28980N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28980N\"></sup>did I commit a sin in humbling myself so that you might be exalted, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28980O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28980O\"></sup>I preached God's gospel to you free of charge?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I robbed other churches by accepting support from them in order to serve you.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when I was with you and was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28982P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28982P\"></sup>in need, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28982Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28982Q\"></sup>I did not burden anyone, for the brothers who came from Macedonia <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28982R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28982R\"></sup>supplied my need. So I refrained and will refrain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28982S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28982S\"></sup>from burdening you in any way.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28983T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28983T\"></sup>As the truth of Christ is in me, this boasting of mine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28983U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28983U\"></sup>will not be silenced in the regions of Achaia.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And why? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28984V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28984V\"></sup>Because I do not love you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28984W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28984W\"></sup>God knows I do!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And what I am doing I will continue to do, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28985X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28985X\"></sup>in order to undermine the claim of those who would like to claim that in their boasted mission they work on the same terms as we do.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For such men are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28986Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28986Y\"></sup>false apostles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28986Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28986Z\"></sup>deceitful workmen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28986AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28986AA\"></sup>disguising themselves as apostles of Christ.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And no wonder, for even Satan disguises himself as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28987AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28987AB\"></sup>an angel of light.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So it is no surprise if his servants, also, disguise themselves as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28988AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28988AC\"></sup>servants of righteousness. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28988AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28988AD\"></sup>Their end will correspond to their deeds.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I repeat, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28989AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28989AE\"></sup>let no one think me foolish. But even if you do, accept me as a fool, so that I too may boast a little.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>What I am saying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28990AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28990AF\"></sup>with this boastful confidence, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28990AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28990AG\"></sup>I say not as the Lord would but as a fool.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Since <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28991AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28991AH\"></sup>many boast according to the flesh, I too will boast.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For you gladly bear with fools, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28992AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28992AI\"></sup>being wise yourselves!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For you bear it if someone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28993AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28993AJ\"></sup>makes slaves of you, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28993AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28993AK\"></sup>devours you, or takes advantage of you, or puts on airs, or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28993AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28993AL\"></sup>strikes you in the face.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To my shame, I must say, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28994AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28994AM\"></sup>we were too weak for that!But whatever anyone else dares to boast of—I am speaking as a fool—I also dare to boast of that.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Are they Hebrews? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28995AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28995AN\"></sup>So am I. Are they Israelites? So am I. Are they offspring of Abraham? So am I.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Are they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28996AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28996AO\"></sup>servants of Christ? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28996AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28996AP\"></sup>I am a better one—I am talking like a madman—with far greater labors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28996AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28996AQ\"></sup>far more imprisonments, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28996AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28996AR\"></sup>with countless beatings, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28996AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28996AS\"></sup>often near death.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Five times I received at the hands of the Jews the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28997AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28997AT\"></sup>forty lashes less one.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Three times I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28998AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28998AU\"></sup>beaten with rods. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28998AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28998AV\"></sup>Once I was stoned. Three times I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28998AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28998AW\"></sup>was shipwrecked; a night and a day I was adrift at sea;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>on frequent journeys, in danger from rivers, danger from robbers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28999AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28999AX\"></sup>danger from my own people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28999AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28999AY\"></sup>danger from Gentiles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-28999AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-28999AZ\"></sup>danger in the city, danger in the wilderness, danger at sea, danger from false brothers;",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29000BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29000BA\"></sup>in toil and hardship, through many a sleepless night, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29000BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29000BB\"></sup>in hunger and thirst, often without food, in cold and exposure.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And, apart from other things, there is the daily pressure on me of my anxiety for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29001BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29001BC\"></sup>all the churches.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29002BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29002BD\"></sup>Who is weak, and I am not weak? Who is made to fall, and I am not indignant?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29003BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29003BE\"></sup>If I must boast, I will boast of the things that show my weakness.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29004BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29004BF\"></sup>The God and Father of the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29004BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29004BG\"></sup>he who is blessed forever, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29004BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29004BH\"></sup>knows that I am not lying.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>At Damascus, the governor under King Aretas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29005BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29005BI\"></sup>was guarding the city of Damascus in order to seize me,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29006BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29006BJ\"></sup>but I was let down in a basket through a window in the wall and escaped his hands."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>I must go on boasting. Though there is nothing to be gained by it, I will go on to visions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29007A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29007A\"></sup>revelations of the Lord.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I know a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29008B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29008B\"></sup>in Christ who fourteen years ago was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29008C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29008C\"></sup>caught up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29008D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29008D\"></sup>the third heaven—whether in the body or out of the body I do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29008E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29008E\"></sup>God knows.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I know that this man was caught up into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29009F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29009F\"></sup>paradise—whether in the body or out of the body I do not know, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29009G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29009G\"></sup>God knows—",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and he heard things that cannot be told, which man may not utter.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On behalf of this man I will boast, but on my own behalf I will not boast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29011H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29011H\"></sup>except of my weaknesses—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>though if I should wish to boast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29012I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29012I\"></sup>I would not be a fool, for I would be speaking the truth; but I refrain from it, so that no one may think more of me than he sees in me or hears from me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29013J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29013J\"></sup>to keep me from becoming conceited because of the surpassing greatness of the revelations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29013K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29013K\"></sup>a thorn was given me in the flesh, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29013L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29013L\"></sup>a messenger of Satan to harass me, to keep me from becoming conceited.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29014M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29014M\"></sup>Three times I pleaded with the Lord about this, that it should leave me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But he said to me, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29015N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29015N\"></sup>“My grace is sufficient for you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29015O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29015O\"></sup>my power is made perfect in weakness.”</span> Therefore I will boast all the more gladly of my weaknesses, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29015P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29015P\"></sup>the power of Christ may rest upon me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29016Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29016Q\"></sup>For the sake of Christ, then, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29016R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29016R\"></sup>I am content with weaknesses, insults, hardships, persecutions, and calamities. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29016S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29016S\"></sup>when I am weak, then I am strong.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29017T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29017T\"></sup>I have been a fool! You forced me to it, for I ought to have been commended by you. For I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29017U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29017U\"></sup>not at all inferior to these super-apostles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29017V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29017V\"></sup>even though I am nothing.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29018W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29018W\"></sup>The signs of a true apostle were performed among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29018X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29018X\"></sup>with utmost patience, with signs and wonders and mighty works.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For in what were you less favored than the rest of the churches, except that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29019Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29019Y\"></sup>I myself did not burden you? Forgive me this wrong!",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Here <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29020Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29020Z\"></sup>for the third time I am ready to come to you. And I will not be a burden, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29020AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29020AA\"></sup>I seek not what is yours but you. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29020AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29020AB\"></sup>children are not obligated to save up for their parents, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29020AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29020AC\"></sup>parents for their children.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29021AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29021AD\"></sup>I will most gladly spend and be spent for your souls. If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29021AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29021AE\"></sup>I love you more, am I to be loved less?",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But granting that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29022AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29022AF\"></sup>I myself did not burden you, I was crafty, you say, and got the better of you by deceit.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Did I take advantage of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29023AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29023AG\"></sup>through any of those whom I sent to you?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29024AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29024AH\"></sup>I urged Titus to go, and sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29024AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29024AI\"></sup>the brother with him. Did Titus take advantage of you? Did we not act in the same spirit? Did we not take the same steps?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Have you been thinking all along that we have been defending ourselves to you? It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29025AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29025AJ\"></sup>in the sight of God that we have been speaking in Christ, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29025AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29025AK\"></sup>all for your upbuilding, beloved.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For I fear that perhaps <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29026AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29026AL\"></sup>when I come I may find you not as I wish, and that you may find me not as you wish—that perhaps there may be quarreling, jealousy, anger, hostility, slander, gossip, conceit, and disorder.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I fear that when I come again my God may humble me before you, and I may have to mourn over many of those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29027AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29027AM\"></sup>who sinned earlier and have not repented of the impurity, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29027AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29027AN\"></sup>sexual immorality, and sensuality that they have practiced."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29028A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29028A\"></sup>This is the third time I am coming to you. Every charge must be established <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29028B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29028B\"></sup>by the evidence of two or three witnesses.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29029C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29029C\"></sup>I warned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29029D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29029D\"></sup>those who sinned before and all the others, and I warn them now while absent, as I did when present on my second visit, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29029E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29029E\"></sup>if I come again I will not spare them—",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>since you seek proof that Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29030F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29030F\"></sup>is speaking in me. He is not weak in dealing with you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29030G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29030G\"></sup>is powerful among you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29031H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29031H\"></sup>he was crucified in weakness, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29031I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29031I\"></sup>lives by the power of God. For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29031J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29031J\"></sup>we also are weak in him, but in dealing with you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29031K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29031K\"></sup>we will live with him by the power of God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Examine yourselves, to see whether you are in the faith. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29032L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29032L\"></sup>Test yourselves. Or do you not realize this about yourselves, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29032M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29032M\"></sup>Jesus Christ is in you?—unless indeed you fail to meet the test!",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I hope you will find out that we have not failed the test.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But we pray to God that you may not do wrong—not that we may appear to have met the test, but that you may do what is right, though we may seem to have failed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For we cannot do anything against the truth, but only for the truth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we are glad when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29036N\"></sup>we are weak and you are strong. Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29036O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29036O\"></sup>restoration is what we pray for.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For this reason I write these things while I am away from you, that when I come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29037P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29037P\"></sup>I may not have to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29037Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29037Q\"></sup>severe in my use of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29037R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29037R\"></sup>the authority that the Lord has given me for building up and not for tearing down.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Finally, brothers, rejoice. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29038S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29038S\"></sup>Aim for restoration, comfort one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29038T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29038T\"></sup>agree with one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29038U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29038U\"></sup>live in peace; and the God of love and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29038V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29038V\"></sup>peace will be with you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29039W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29039W\"></sup>Greet one another with a holy kiss.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29040X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29040X\"></sup>All the saints greet you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29041Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29041Y\"></sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus Christ and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29041Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29041Z\"></sup>the love of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-29041AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-29041AA\"></sup>the fellowship of the Holy Spirit be with you all."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;